column5: Did another annual 7 day trip into the park on trout opener and it was as to be expected, awesome! Lots of good food and trout. Weather was awesome and so was the peace and quiet. I'll just post some pics.and say that I will be sad the day when the body doesn't let me explore trout country. Love this stuff!
My apologies for the double post .......ugh!
I too, do fear the day we're too old and tired to play like we do.  Pack it all in now, Enjoy your park reports Matt.
Nice going.  Dont do as many canoe trips as I used to sure have some good memories paddelin.
